course_description: Development of specific fitness components utilizing cardio exercise equipment (e.g., elliptical trainers, stationary bikes, rowing ergometers, tracks). Use of exercise equipment in all classes is dependent upon availability and instructor preference. Fulfills the PPF requirement.
prerequisites: All students who have fulfilled the PPF requirement of (1) PPF MAY NOT enroll into a second PPF course.
